Jive,provides,social,networking,services,for,businesses,It,can,be,used,within,companies,to,help,employees,sync,up,and,work,together,or,it,can,be,used,externally,to,support,customer,communities,that,improve,service,support,and,customer,satisfaction,Jive,s,REST,API,provides,a,comprehensive,set,of,functions,for,interacting,with,a,Jive,community,using,GET,PUT,POST,and,DELETE,calls,The,JavaScript,API,enables,developers,to,interact,with,their,Jive,instance,from,within,a,Jive,App